high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Look up and take the mug out of the cabinet.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge in front of the tomato. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Open the leftmost bottom cabinet and place the mug in it, behind the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the fridge then move to your right until you face the counter to the left of the stove with the phones and the yellow handled knife.
Look up and open the cupboard and grab the mug that's up there then close the doors.
Take a small step backwards then turn left and walk to the fridge then turn right to face it.
Chill the mug in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Take a small step to your right.
Open the cupboard that's to the right of the fridge then put the mug in there then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the front of the cabinet above the sink on the left of the stove.
Take out the coffee mug in the cabinet.
Turn left and go to the front of the refrigerator on the right.
Remove the mug from the refrigerator after cooling in it.
Move over right to the front of the cabinet on the left of the dishwasher.
Place the mug behind the green sponge in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled coffee mug in the cabinet
